            {%- else -%}
              <p>To ensure your {{ collection.title }} continues to radiate positive energy and maintain its physical brilliance, a balanced care routine is essential.</p>
              <h4 style="margin-top: 20px;">🧼 Physical Cleaning</h4>
              <p>Clean your gemstone once a month using a soft brush and a solution of mild, phosphate-free dish soap in lukewarm water. Gently scrub the underside where dust often accumulates. Rinse with filtered water and pat dry with a lint-free cloth.</p>
              <h4 style="margin-top: 20px;">🌙 Spiritual Cleansing (Energization)</h4>
              <p>To remove accumulated negative vibes, place your gemstone in a bowl of pure rock salt or leave it under the soft light of a full moon overnight. This refreshes the stone's natural vibrations.</p>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Panel 6: FAQ -->
        <div class="collection-tabs__panel" id="tab-faq" role="tabpanel">
          <h2 class="collection-tabs__panel-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <div class="collection-tabs__panel-content rte">
            {%- if collection.metafields.custom.content_faq != blank -%}
              {{ collection.metafields.custom.content_faq }}
            {%- elsif has_mapped_content -%}
              {{ mapped_faq }}
            {%- else -%}
              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <strong>Are these stones Lab-Grown?</strong>
                <p>No. We deal exclusively in 100% natural, earth-mined gemstones. We do not sell synthetic or "lab-grown" alternatives.</p>
              </div>
              <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <strong>How do I know the stone is authentic?</strong>
                <p>Every single gemstone in this collection comes with an independent lab certificate from a government-recognized gemological laboratory confirming its natural status and origin.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <strong>Is the stone already energized?</strong>
                <p>Yes, all our stones undergo a traditional Vedic "Pran-Pratishtha" or energization process at a holy shrine before they are shipped to ensure they are active for remedial purposes.</p>
              </div>
            {%- endif -%}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

